904
00:54:09,000 --> 00:54:11,125
He gave us a couple of
pieces...information

905
00:54:11,209 --> 00:54:13,167
during that early phase.

906
00:54:15,584 --> 00:54:17,834
But then he stopped talking.

907
00:54:17,918 --> 00:54:19,375
When he regained
his strength,

908
00:54:19,459 --> 00:54:22,083
he stopped talking.

909
00:54:22,167 --> 00:54:24,250
And we became convinced

910
00:54:24,334 --> 00:54:27,626
that we had to come up
with a new alternative

911
00:54:27,709 --> 00:54:29,584
to doing this
because it was not working.

912
00:54:52,667 --> 00:54:56,083
Eight of the 12 techniques,
in my humble opinion,

913
00:54:56,167 --> 00:54:58,167
were pretty wimpy stuff.

914
00:54:58,250 --> 00:55:00,876
You know, like, slapping.
Give me a break.

915
00:55:00,959 --> 00:55:03,209
OK, it might be unpleasant
to slap somebody,

916
00:55:03,292 --> 00:55:05,000
but it's not torture.

917
00:55:05,083 --> 00:55:06,792
Grabbing someone
from the lapel,

918
00:55:06,876 --> 00:55:09,834
bringing him in to you may
be unpleasant

919
00:55:09,918 --> 00:55:11,042
and it's
an attention grabber,

920
00:55:11,125 --> 00:55:12,834
but it's not torture.

921
00:55:12,918 --> 00:55:14,209
We didn't ask for this.

922
00:55:14,292 --> 00:55:16,209
We did not ask
to get attacked.

923
00:55:16,292 --> 00:55:17,500
They did it.

924
00:55:17,584 --> 00:55:22,459
And so if we can't make them
uncomfortable to save lives,

925
00:55:22,542 --> 00:55:24,459
then...we've missed
the boat here.

926
00:55:24,542 --> 00:55:27,459
I believe that
the intention was,

927
00:55:27,542 --> 00:55:29,959
"We can never allow
this to happen.

928
00:55:30,042 --> 00:55:32,167
Let's do whatever
needs to be done."

929
00:55:32,250 --> 00:55:34,959
They're straight-up haters.

930
00:55:35,042 --> 00:55:36,375
There is no reasoning
with them.

931
00:55:36,459 --> 00:55:40,626
Some individuals who were
at the time in places

932
00:55:40,709 --> 00:55:43,500
to make decisions
believe that the only reason

933
00:55:43,584 --> 00:55:45,417
you deal with
these individuals is by

934
00:55:45,500 --> 00:55:46,876
techniques like this.

935
00:55:46,959 --> 00:55:48,959
If you deal with some
of the hardcore...

936
00:55:49,042 --> 00:55:52,876
our detainees...they
might have become compliant

937
00:55:52,959 --> 00:55:54,876
and then maybe jovial
and engaging,

938
00:55:54,959 --> 00:55:56,876
but if you ask them,
"What are you gonna do

