00:57:02,292 --> 00:57:03,792
between being an expert

962
00:57:03,876 --> 00:57:07,751
behind a desk and being
a field expert.

963
00:57:08,876 --> 00:57:12,542
You can't argue
with success.

964
00:57:12,626 --> 00:57:14,667
And the fact
of the matter is

965
00:57:14,751 --> 00:57:17,000
that we were extremely
successful.

966
00:57:17,083 --> 00:57:19,918
Once we started
using the techniques

967
00:57:20,000 --> 00:57:26,334
