1002
00:59:12,083 --> 00:59:13,459
it was just a few weeks.

1003
00:59:13,542 --> 00:59:15,167
This program evolved

1004
00:59:15,250 --> 00:59:17,792
because, you know,
some of the stuff

1005
00:59:17,876 --> 00:59:19,959
