part of this

1008
00:59:26,375 --> 00:59:28,417
and...I shouldn't be even
a witness for this.

1009
00:59:28,500 --> 00:59:30,000
And I put it
to our headquarters,

1010
00:59:30,083 --> 00:59:31,876
