1016
00:59:40,334 --> 00:59:42,209
I understand people are
uncomfortable with this,

1017
00:59:42,292 --> 00:59:44,792
but the options
we had were not very good.

1018
01:00:20,292 --> 01:00:22,667
In the aftermath
of 9/11, people expected

