writing this blog

1388
01:23:50,167 --> 01:23:51,667
and getting himself
in trouble.

1389
01:23:51,751 --> 01:23:53,209
Over a period of months,

1390
01:23:53,292 --> 01:23:54,584
he becomes one of

1391
